{"id": 7035, "source": "pestle", "subject": "chemistry", "course": null, "level": "SL", "paper": "1", "year": "2017", "session": "17M", "subtopic": "1-3-reacting-masses-and-volumes", "title": "17M.1.SL.TZ1.4", "topic_id": "1", "source_url": "https://pestle.pages.dev/app/", "question_html": "<div class=\"question\">\n<p>What is the expression for the volume of hydrogen gas, in dm<sup>3</sup>, produced at STP when 0.30 g of magnesium reacts with excess hydrochloric acid solution?</p>\n<p>Mg(s) + 2HCl(aq) → MgCl<sub>2</sub>(aq) + H<sub>2</sub>(g)</p>\n<p>Molar volume of an ideal gas at STP = 22.7 dm<sup>3</sup><span class=\"mjpage\"><math alttext=\"\\,\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n<mspace width=\"thinmathspace\"></mspace>\n</math></span>mol<sup>−1</sup></p>\n<p>A.     <span class=\"mjpage\"><math alttext=\"\\frac{{0.30 \\times 2 \\times 22.7}}{{24.31}}\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n<mfrac>\n<mrow>\n<mn>0.30</mn>\n<mo>×</mo>\n<mn>2</mn>\n<mo>×</mo>\n<mn>22.7</mn>\n</mrow>\n<mrow>\n<mn>24.31</mn>\n</mrow>\n</mfrac>\n</math></span></p>\n<p>B.     <span class=\"mjpage\"><math alttext=\"\\frac{{0.30 \\times 22.7}}{{24.31}}\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n<mfrac>\n<mrow>\n<mn>0.30</mn>\n<mo>×</mo>\n<mn>22.7</mn>\n</mrow>\n<mrow>\n<mn>24.31</mn>\n</mrow>\n</mfrac>\n</math></span></p>\n<p>C.     <span class=\"mjpage\"><math alttext=\"\\frac{{0.30 \\times 24.31}}{{22.7}}\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n<mfrac>\n<mrow>\n<mn>0.30</mn>\n<mo>×</mo>\n<mn>24.31</mn>\n</mrow>\n<mrow>\n<mn>22.7</mn>\n</mrow>\n</mfrac>\n</math></span></p>\n<p>D.     <span class=\"mjpage\"><math alttext=\"\\frac{{0.30 \\times 22.7}}{{24.31 \\times 2}}\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n<mfrac>\n<mrow>\n<mn>0.30</mn>\n<mo>×</mo>\n<mn>22.7</mn>\n</mrow>\n<mrow>\n<mn>24.31</mn>\n<mo>×</mo>\n<mn>2</mn>\n</mrow>\n</mfrac>\n</math></span></p>\n</div>", "solution_html": "<div class=\"question\">\n<p>B</p>\n</div>", "examiners_html": "<div class=\"question\">\n[N/A]\n</div>"}